// Input handling

// keyboard controls simulate analog measurements with multiple taps
// q or u key increases left thruster by 10%
// z or m key decreases left thruster by 10%

// e or o key increases right thruster by 10%
// c or . key decreases right thruster by 10%

// w or i key increases elevator by 10%
// s or k key decreases elevator  by 10%

// a or j key increases rudder by 10%
// d or l key decreases rudder by 10%

// r or p key increases aft thruster by 10%
// v or / key decreases rudder by 10%
